  abstract = {We present the discovery of two Saturn-mass companions to HD 
108147 and HD 168746. Both belong to the
lightest ever discovered planets. The minimum mass of the companion to
HD 168746 is of only 0.77 the mass of Saturn and its
orbital period is 6.4 days. The companion to HD
108147 orbits its parent star in 10.9 days and its minimum
